{
  "stem": "9730.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at the funeral, our divisional chaplain read-- who also spoke German still read a eulogy, which actually was something that Gerda Weissmann wrote at that time, which was an ode to the American liberators, an ode of thanks for liberating them.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, most of them, of course, pretended that they had never heard of-- of such conditions and didn't know that this type of thing existed, as was the reaction in almost any other part of Germany.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To the people who live nearby, even the people who in the death camps could smell it in the air, they all pretended they didn't really know what was going on.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] also, he-- you know, he recited the Jewish prayers and the kaddish.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The factory?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the factory was actually in bad repair, because it hadn't been used in some time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it was at one time used to make bicycle trains, and-- but hadn't been used in a number of years so that it had deteriorated.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we went back four years ago, we still found the same places and the same halls and the same rooms.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and they-- they hadn't deteriorated much worse than they were in those days, although they were slightly better in those days.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were all gone by that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- so we-- no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right, and see if we couldn't nurse them back to health.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I-- I stayed in the area for, oh, perhaps a couple of weeks, during which time I-- I visited as often as I could.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when-- then, of course, after the war, at that time, it was already clear that this area would ultimately be occupied by Russian troops.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
